{"tid":37083,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"（癡線）Tesla郵輪碼頭危駕 高速逆線飆100米","createTime":"2016-12-13T06:27:12.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-13T09:15:39.000Z","uid":22675,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"fd676b1ad8184fc524cafad44bed40d1d62b0e1e","tid":37083,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-13T06:27:12.000Z","msg":"啟德郵輪碼頭上月發生奪命車禍後，警方東九龍交通特遣隊加強在附近一帶巡查，打擊高速駕駛情況。今早11時，警方隱形戰車在承豐道巡查時，發現一輛白色Tesla電動跑車在路上風馳電掣，沿途多次爬頭，更以時速110公里逆線行車逾100米。現場車速限制為時速50公里。<br />\n隱形戰車尾隨追截，至郵輪碼頭停車場將Tesla截停，當場拘捕車上一名中年男子，涉嫌危險駕駛等罪名。據悉，被捕男子報稱職業為一名司機，並非Tesla車主。<br />\n另外，昨午2時許，警方亦在承豐道截停一輛以時速133公里行駛的Tesla跑車，並拘捕一人。<br />\n上月2日， 一名23歲單車青年在承豐道，遭一輛逆線行駛的P牌黑色寶馬撞倒，送院後重傷不治。"},{"pid":"913c01d7e49b42eb067e7b7b1a287e0f6421b4dd","tid":37083,"uid":61864,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-13T06:28:11.000Z","msg":"輕輕地留名"},{"pid":"7e4c2724897ee5aabe972fe271da4c6fb273fc7f","tid":37083,"uid":90,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-13T06:28:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"004867cd65525d25b1d8ca7c595b5429bcce3068","tid":37083,"uid":39750,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-13T06:30:18.000Z","msg":"3秒都唔駛就上到100 係香港用係難啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b33fe1443cd0fe634dbc984790f8957628e68c3c","tid":37083,"uid":42452,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-13T06:38:47.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=LpaLgF1uLB8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DLpaLgF1uLB8&d=dMw%2FSDUuvxnscJWfGjG4d2N6obqfy%2FNc7jg2IsrTbnE%3D&h=b4fa8c4a\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=LpaLgF1uLB8</a><br />\n大家可以睇下tesla有幾快"},{"pid":"c84895e3191292b64fb3dd776884226e67bf65fd","tid":37083,"uid":33263,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-13T06:55:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b58b7163538d59290218744596cabca392605a8f","tid":37083,"uid":17103,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-13T07:03:26.000Z","msg":"玩得逆線都預左停牌"},{"pid":"00117c5074a63b321f5a3024e5734dd6cf468a6a","tid":37083,"uid":6799,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-13T07:05:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>玩得逆線都預左停牌</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n逆線仲要超一倍速"},{"pid":"b909ddba024cfd8c62591e73e6001845ce1c1c34","tid":37083,"uid":8687,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-13T07:19:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/12/13/151910_b3349bf8af1f248157f5c992ed701d53.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F12%2F13%2F151910_b3349bf8af1f248157f5c992ed701d53.jpg&h=436bb26a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3d9e969926ebf303561b9ce5eac80c6aa6ae21e1","tid":37083,"uid":12021,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-13T07:25:40.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"a635e36021186110845bd5cbdb9e6631f6fbd505","tid":37083,"uid":33878,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-13T07:25:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"056e2cc1db18e716ffa78a4c4bed84352c25791b","tid":37083,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-13T09:15:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}